有行政費係正常 唔需要將呢樣野惡魔化 你唔出錢請人 有冇咁多義工去幫手handle啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算有又e唔effective<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大機構嘅好處係可以take advantage of economies of scale 雖然我都唔知捐比大定細有用啲 我捐錢個心態係預左唔係捐100蚊就100蚊都去晒啲受助者身上 畢竟啲ngo員工都係要出糧 連登仔自問肯唔肯唔收錢長期去做義工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得捐左有幫到合理程度就夠 所以個點就係在於啲錢係唔係用得其所同透明度夠唔夠 唔係要佢完全無行政費"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪就係講緊太多<br />\n$100有$90"},{"pid":"e671093dbaf333339052c63a7b666d891767b785","tid":1146101,"uid":144464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ab4c24ad8b57e4ec53b21df78544cdeec8e27d3","tid":1146101,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9a8d3a93d515660ac847b476238eaf30a0fd879","tid":1146101,"uid":144464,"like":129,"dislike":16,"score":113,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"養埋我啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:36:22.000Z","msg":"去慈善機構做高層咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"你指樂詩會？？"},{"pid":"f99c81383ace5bb54a2757cd609162c30489644f","tid":1146101,"uid":236995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:41:28.000Z","msg":"我都想俾個空姐助養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9b897a61f15e5f792f50372d0c04090596c2d5","tid":1146101,"uid":31847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"係天使呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479e9a1fc930e8270fd431be4f99210319a4a538","tid":1146101,"uid":6031,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:51:15.000Z","msg":"（題外話）<br />\n諗起之前睇過篇嘢<br />\n話呢啲助養計劃其實即係做幫兇<br />\n<br />\n先勿論啲助養基金有幾多成去到個助養兒童到，就算十成去哂，其實都無補於事，甚至係令第三國家貧窮情況惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為夾硬養大啲細路，但冇政策去限制佢哋生仔，同時缺乏性教育，助養變相令佢哋繼續生更多「助養兒童」出黎，無限loop，越做越多，個餅越黎越大。<br />\n<br />\n得益者就係樂施會呢啲「慈善機構」，永續助養計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正需要做嘅係教育，但慈善機構似乎冇點喺呢方面下苦工"},{"pid":"4e4104bfd08c2af521ad538b5d9fd3453592117e","tid":1146101,"uid":33899,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"339f1c4a05655cda7b57fee8a9d52ddd305a8901","tid":1146101,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:59:24.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以養你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆街死全族啦南亞賤種<br />\n又想強姦人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0df0be9d46897624b7e0cc24f32f77841bf38142","tid":1146101,"uid":196751,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"我真係說服唔到自己去幫一班人類害蟲去執手尾<br />\n佢地大左又係亂咁生,真正幫佢地應該好似流浪貓狗咁幫佢地絕育<br />\n我寧願捐錢比動物組織"},{"pid":"421598d70e3e72c75e8548b4408800320f3d9031","tid":1146101,"uid":226296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3b810a297394f9c8a322fa5e3af3d0da850d60","tid":1146101,"uid":131731,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人知嗰2000蚊最後有幾多會畀到嗰8位小朋友?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caef37cb4e91d2819fc6f417a32613a0dae6c46","tid":1146101,"uid":76845,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2dbbdc5888c254c9db852f5a6274d265b355771e","tid":1